Orbi bhaxentlea kanneancho namvajil'lo jhelo. Hachem mull orbi namv ‘olf loiloh – vo-loiloh’ (olifoloiloh) oxem asun inglixint ‘orebiyon naitts enttorottenomentt’ani ‘von thauzondd ondd von naitts’ oxim namvam ruddh asat. Eka prastavik kothasutrant torekovar kotha guthompachem somskrit ‘ponchtontr’ va ‘xukosptoti’ hanche bharti-i tontr orebiyon naitts ani ‘von thauzondd ondd von naitts’ oxim namvam ruddh asat. Eka prastavik kothasutrant torekovar kotha guthompachem somskrit ‘ponchtontr’ va ‘xukosptoti’ hanche bharti-i tontr orebiyon naitts hatunt disun yeta. Hem kothatontr ostonti sahity somikxent ‘ramen ertselung’ hea zormon namvan vollkhotat.

Orebiyon naittsochea kothanchea sankhllechi fattbhum-i oxiH irannocho raza xohroyar aple rannyechea vyobhicharak lagun tiddkota ani purai bail-zaticho sudd gheupachem tharaita.Dekhun, dor rati eke baile vangdda raza logn zata ani sokallim fuddem tika jitich marun uddoita. Razachea nojirachi choli xahzadi (xahrazad) sogle strizatik vattaupachi ek yukt sodun kaddtta ani bapaichi som'mti gheun raza kodden logn zata. Ratik ti razak ani apli dhaktti bhoinn duniazad hankam ek kanni sangta. Aple kotha sangpache huxarokayen kanni ordich dourun ti ratichem razachem mon kannyechea fuddlea bhagant ghuspaun dourota. Kannyecho mukhavelo vantto aikupa khatir dusrea disa raza tika jiudan dita oxem dor fantodder ghoddtta. Tinnem ek hozar rati sangil'lea kanneamni raza samko rongun vota. Tachem kalliz pajhrota ani to aplo krur vichar monantlean kaddun uddoita.

Orebiyon naittsochem prochlit svorup otthravea xotmanant sidhd zalem. Hea kanneanchea lekhkavixim koslich mahiti mellil'li na. Ol-mosudi hea orbi lekhkachea ‘muruzujh-jhhob’(947) hea gronthant ‘hozar ofsana’ oso ul'lekh melltta, oxem nobia aebott hannem 1949 to nodrek haddlem. Hachevelean farsi bhaxentosun heo kotha orbi bhaxent aileo oxem aebottachem mot asa. He kotheche choukttichem mull bharti-i asot oxem-i ek mot asa.

Bharot, irann, irak, turkostan ani ijipt hanche kodden sombondit oxe kaim kothabhag hea kothant aspautat. Hatuntolim choddxim vixex namam orbi, muslim' ani kaim bharti-i toxench yuropi-i asat. Hatuntole kaim kotha prosong chin ani bharot hanga ghoddil'le asle tori kothanche bhitl'le bhag ani prernna ossol orbi ani islami asat. Kalvipreasacho dox legit ‘orebiyon naitts’ kanneamni disun yeta. Irannchea xohroyar razacho kalkhondd islamopurv manlear bogdad bosra ani koiro hea islam' uprantchea kallant namnek pavil'lea xarancho ul'lekh vipryost dista. Kofi ani tombakhu onukroman choudavea ani sollavea xotmana meren ijiptant oprichit axil'lim. Punn tancho ul'lekh hea kothamni aila. Ijiptantole pondravea xenkddeantole xixttachar ani chaliriti ‘orebiyon naitts’ hatunt disun yetat. Ghoddye heach kallant tatuntleo mull kotha purai korun ani tatunt noveo kotha ghalun tancho jhelo kela asunk zai. Kurann soddun orbi sahiteantolo khoinchoch gronth itli namna ani lokpriyota zoddunk pauna na. Tatuntleo ‘olibaba ani challis chor’ ‘ol'laud'din ani zaducho divo’, ‘sindbadacheo bhomvddeo’ heo kotha soglleank porichit asat.

Mull orob bhaxentleo heo kotha kaveatmok oxa kuddkea-kuddkeamni rochleat. Teo kotha kothna khatir ani khasa surant gaupa khatir rochlea asunk zai. Hea soglea kothamni vibhagonni oxi korum yetaH 1. Porikotha ani kalponik kotha. 2. Bogdadocho sultan harun-ol-roxid ani tacho prodhan hanche kodden sombondit axil'leo mogacheo ani oprupancheo kanneo. Hatunt itihasik sotyona. 3. Modhyomourgi-i lokam kodden sombondit axil'leo hamsealleo ani thoddeobhovo xringarik kotha hanchi rochna teravea te sollavea xotkant, mamluk sultananche mustint koiro (ol-kahiroh) hanga zali asunk zai. 4. Sahsokotha. 5. Bodhpor kotha 6. Akheayika ani dontkotha hancher adarit kotha. 7. Dhormik kotha.

Oxem vorgikoronn korun legit orebiyon naitts kothant ekatmota ani ekvakyota disun yena. Sindbadchea sofrinchi kotha tor svotontroponnan rochlea ani magir tatunt ghalea.Vafmoyin gunnout'teche nodren tatunt vixmota disun yetda. Thoddeo kotha bondist ani kolatmok dhortecheo asat tor kaim kothamni rochna xithil dista. Heo kotha ghottna prodhan asun vyoktichitronn sthul svorupanchem asa. Punn kothnokouxly, obhinou kolponavilas ani monis sobhavachem mormogonean hea gunnank lagun heo oprupacheo odbhutormy kotha somvsarobhor lokpriy zaleo.

‘orebiyon naitts’ cho poilo onnkar antvan galam hannem perisak 1704 te 1717 hea kallant french bhaxent kelo ani yuropi-i lokank hea kothanchi poili vollokh korun dili. Mull orbi bhaxeuylean kel'lea galanchea onnkarache her yuropiyon bhasantuy onnkar zale. Zormon lekhok habixtt hannem mull orbi kotha somhita zormonitlea breslovo hanga chhapli (1825-43) ani 1840t ticho zormon onnkar ujvaddak haddlo. Kairo hanga 1835 to chhapil'lea orbi protivelean i. Ddoblyu. Len hea obheasokan dorjedar punn opurnn inglix onnkar (1839-41)ujvaddak haddlo. Hea kothank ‘orebiyon naitts enttorottenomentt’ hem namv tannench dilem. Kolokt'ta hangche orbi proticher (1839-41) adarit inglix onnkar zon pen hannem kelo. (1882-84). Sor richrdd ef. Borttonchea 16 khonddantlea onnkarak (1885-89) upatt lokpriyota mell'lli. Je.Si. Mordrusocho french onnkar (1899) legit khub lokpriy zalo. Yuropiyon bhasantlea soglleant unch pamvddeacho man i. Littmonchea 6 khonddantlea zormon onnkarak (1921-28) fauta.

Orebiyon naittsoche somhitevixinchi ani her prosnanchi chikitsa ddi. Bi. Mekddonaldd hea omerikon obheasokachea gronthant ailea. Hea kothantlea bogdadi ani ijipxiyon oxa don tthollok storancho obheas egostt myulorchea vivechonant aspauta.

Krixnnoxastri chipllunnokoran 1861 to inglixintlean hea kothancho moratthi onnkar korpak survat keli. Vixnnuxastri chipllunnokar ani hori krixnn damle hamnni taka hatbhar laitokoch 1890 to ‘orbi bhaxetil suros vo chomtkarik goxtti’ pustok rupan ujvaddak ailo. Tanchi 6 bhagamni novi aurit'ti 1957 to ujvaddak aili. ‘orebiyon naitts’cho moratthi onnkar tryom.Pu.Thorat, va.Go. Aptte hamnni-i kela. Sor borttonchea mull inglix bhaxentlea ‘orebiyon naitts’cho 1975 to goura dexpandde hamnni 11 khonddant kel'lo moratthi onnkar khub lokpriy zalo.



